dred_day_avg":177.94392,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":315.65,"all_time_low":92.5,"long_business_summary":"Avax Apparels and Ornaments Limited engages in the wholesale trading and manufacturing of knitted cloth in India. It operates through two segments, Wholesale Trading of Knitted Cloth and Online Retail of Silver Ornaments. The company offers cotton, crepe, denim, linen, satin, synthetic, and velvet fabrics, as well as flat or jersey knit and purl knit fabrics used in manufacturing of ladies and gents' jackets. It is involved in the online retail of silver ornaments and jewelry through blushines.com, an e-commerce portal. The company was formerly known as Avax Soft Technologies Limited and changed its name to Avax Apparels and Ornaments Limited in June 2023. Avax Apparels and Ornaments Limited was incorporated in 2005 and is based in New Delhi, India."}}